## Caveats

### Nameservers

Can not be used in conjunction with INWX nameservers.


## Import

INWX DNSSEC keys can be imported using the domain name and digest e.g.,

```sh
 $ pulumi import inwx:index/dnssecKey:DnssecKey example_com example.com/4E1243BD22C66E76C2BA9EDDC1F91394E57F9F83
```

